                            <comment id="477809" author="gerrit" created="Mon, 10 Nov 2025 19:49:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&quot;James Simmons &amp;lt;jsimmons@infradead.org&amp;gt;&quot; uploaded a new patch: &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62479&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62479&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
